FT  06 AUG 94 / UK Company News: Finsbury Smaller asset value up 11%
Net asset value at Finsbury Smaller Companies was 167.2p per share at the
end of June, compared with 150.2p a year earlier. The 11.3 per cent increase
compared with a gain of 8.4 per cent in the Hoare Govett Smaller Companies
Index.
Net revenue increased from Pounds 254,000 to Pounds 320,000. Earnings per
share fell from 2.2p to 2p, and an interim dividend of 1.2p (1.1p) is
declared.
